title: Question 1
question: The back is located and delimited by:

options.label: Anterior surface of the trunk, below the skull and above the coccyx

question: Which of the following structures is not located on the back?

options.label: Spine
Ribs
Scapulas

options.label: Axial skeleton and appendicular skeleton

32 vertebrae, 23 of which are pre-sacral

01 vertebral body, 01 vertebral arch and 07 processes

06 cervical, 12 thoracic, and 06 lumbar
